for start this program print in console (she must be located in CLASSPATH. if your console located in project directory print: cd .\src\fourthTask\)
java .\Main.java arg1 arg2
where arg1 - it's string which will be modified
and arg2 it's count of spaces


for better debugging replace variable "space" in Main.class to another char
Example:
    java .\Main.java "Hello     world!!!  It's ME    "   "3"